            <td class="section__table__datum">$2.4M</td>
            <td class="section__table__datum">Up 4%</td>
          </tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="page__section profile__section">
    <header class="section__header">
      <h3 class="section__head">Export possiblities</h3>
    </header>
    <p class="section__intro">We've found that countries which export complex products grow faster than those which export simple products. Using the similarity map we built in the section above, we've highlighted  high potential products for {{model.name}}, ranked by which have the highest combination of opportunity and complexity.</p>
    <div class="section__spacemod">
      <div class="section__spacemod__vizmod">
        <div class="section__spacemod__legend">
          <ul class="section__spacemod__legend__list">
            <li class="section__spacemod__legend__item">Non-export</li>
            <li class="section__spacemod__legend__item">Export</li>
            <li class="section__spacemod__legend__item">Similarity link</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="section__spacemod__vizwrap"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="section__spacemod__listmod">
        <h4 class="section__spacemod__listmod__head">High potential exports for {{model.name}}</h4>
        <ol class="section__spacemod__listmod__ol">
          <li class="section__spacemod__listmod__item">Slag wool, rock wool, and similar mineral wools</li>
          <li class="section__spacemod__listmod__item">Lifting, handling, (un)loading machinery (ex. elevators, escalators, conveyors)</li>
          <li class="section__spacemod__listmod__item">Other plastic plates, sheets, film, foil and strip</li>
          <li class="section__spacemod__listmod__item">Printed pictures and photographs</li>
          <li class="section__spacemod__listmod__item">Other fermented beverages (ex. cider) and mixtures</li>
        </ol>
      </div>
      <footer class="section__spacemod__footer">
        <p class="section__spacemod__footer__p">Note that the list is dynamically generated. Not all exports may make sense given local conditions not captured in our measure of product similarity.</p>
      </footer>
    </div>
